node.title: Child among five people injured in multi-vehicle crash
node.alt: Emergency services surround overturned truck and crashed vehicles.
node.description: Emergency services are working to free multiple people trapped after a major crash on the Calder Freeway, north-west of Melbourne.
node.content: ["Emergency services are working to free multiple people trapped after a major crash on the Calder Freeway, north-west of Melbourne.", "Police say a truck hit several cars just after 2:30pm at the Diggers Rest-Bulla Road overpass.", "Five people needed medical care at the scene.", "A\u00a0child has been taken to the Royal Children's Hospital and another person is being treated at the Royal Melbourne Hospital.", "The freeway's city-bound lanes are closed at Bulla-Diggers Rest Road.", "More to come."]
